Company Overview of Knighthead Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Knighthead Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It manages separate accounts for its clients. The firm invests in public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. For its equity investments it invests in the undervalued stocks. For its fixed income investments the firm invests in the securities of distressed companies. It employs fundamental analysis with bottom up stock picking approach. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It invests in diversified sectors. Knighthead Capital Management, LLC was founded in 2008 and is based in New York, New York.


1140 Avenue of the Americas12th FloorNew York, NY 10036United StatesFounded in 2008



Phone: 212-356-2900

